## Description {#details}

Structs for dyld chained fixups.

<a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/macho/dyld-chained-fixups-header">dyld&#95;chained&#95;fixups&#95;header</a> is the data pointed to by LC&#95;DYLD&#95;CHAINED&#95;FIXUPS load command.
